GIVE: Give an item to another character

Syntax: give <item> to <target>

DESCRIPTION:
  Transfers an item from your inventory to another player or NPC in the
  same room. Some NPCs will react to receiving specific items (e.g., the
  falconer accepts a leather glove).

EXAMPLES:
  give leather glove to falconer
  give credits to thurtea

SEE ALSO: take, drop, inventory
